  <li>
    <p>Some days later Cottard met him in the street and greeted him with the <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="hail-fellow-well-met"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(非常友好地)</code></b> manner that he now used on all occasions.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>“It’s no good counting on the <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="red-tape"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(繁文缛节/官僚习气)</code></b> merchants. They couldn’t understand if they tried.”</p>
