  <li>
    <p>In one of the cafés he visited he was actually taken for a stoolpigeon and curtly <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="sent about his business"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(被打发去办事)</code></b>. It was not until he happened to meet Cottard at Rieux’s place that he made a little headway.</p>
